channel.title: [PI] Map Data
channel.description:
So I went into Taverly Dungeon and I found all the walls, rocks, decorations, etc...were missing. This isn't the only place that is missing mapdata, there's the Coroporeal Beast Lair, Lumbridge, Port Sarim...etc...the thing is I don't know how to pack the Taverly Map data in. So if someone could help me that would be great. I'm having the same problem as this guy, I looked through his thread but it just says he fixed it, no solution. :/ [url=http://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/rs2-client/help/492267-fixing-taverly-dungeon-s.html]http://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/rs2-client/help/492267-fixing-taverly-dungeon-s.html[/url] [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/n2efbk.png[/img]
That picture is not mine by the way, took from his thread. Same thing though.
